4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring specialists, regardless of prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 18 students per class. Participants gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and threat intelligence. Certification upon completion is provided and recognized by multiple institutions. The course materials are available in both English and Spanish, tailored to the campus's language of instruction. For further details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop